text: @DanGheesling What we do in the shadows (on prime)
To everyone: "What We Do in the Shadows" is available on Amazon Prime!  You are welcome. #vampireroommates #werewolvesnotswearwolves
Listening to The Replacements and thinking about Minneapolis today.
My new lovely scented candles arrived! So pretty! Thanks @miltonandmargie https://t.co/tmqrbLQy89
People still make (and burn) microwave popcorn at work? Gross.
A squirrel walked across the street with me at the crosswalk. I wonder if he learned that it is safe to cross when a human does?
I am really bad at peeling hard-boiled eggs.
Went running 2 days in a row for the first time in forever! Hope to be able to do a 5K by Thanksgiving!
Today (after several years) our office regained the ability to print double-sided. #feelslike1994 #savethetrees
Great food tonight outside Epic! Thanks @RoamingBullCO ! https://t.co/uh6Vjv49FA
Making decorations for Olympics viewing party! #RioOlympics2016 #FunWithFlags #Crayola https://t.co/kKP7UkgpFi
Love hanging out with these guys! #dogsitting #playgroup https://t.co/rylBTPzW7n
Snowy morning decision: park far away in covered parking or close to bldg but in covered parking?
Friday afternoon self: too lazy to wash desk coffee cup. Monday morning self: disappointed with Friday self.
Our living room looks so much nicer now! Thanks @CityFloral ! https://t.co/GKff3rgKL2
Getting ready for #studysunday! Hoping the blueberry scones I picked up will help keep me motivated.
